com.netflix.imflibrary

Class MXFUID

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.netflix.imflibrary.MXFUID

  • @Immutable
public final class MXFUID
extends java.lang.Object
    An (immutable) implementation of an MXF UID. Per section 4.1 of st0377-1:2011, a UID is "a generic term which may be used to refer to a UL, UUID, UMID etc."
